column2: so you won't see it listed on my below study plan. Basically
column3: I created a study plan where I am spending 3-5 days on each chapter (depending on the complexity)

column7: Edwell Book and sometimes Andy Crowe Book.  I also have an App on my phone called PMP Genius that has tests organized by chapter.  Please keep in mind that this is my 2nd time reading the PMBOK and Rita book.  Therefore
